  "texts": [
    "Because DevOps focuses on fast delivery, inadequate security measures can lead to issues such as data breaches, malicious intrusions, and reputational damage.",
    "Therefore, by integrating security measures, continuous monitoring and feedback can be ensured to quickly detect and respond to potential security threats.",
    "In addition, compliance requirements and regulations impose higher standards on data security, so ensuring that security is compliant with regulations is also critical.",
    "Ultimately, maintaining security helps reduce costs, as it is often more expensive to fix security breaches than to prevent them.",
    "Therefore, in DevOps practice, ensuring security is an important part of ensuring the quality, compliance, and reliability of software delivery.In the future, DevOps security will continue to evolve and evolve, facing new challenges and opportunities."
  ],
